# Life Of His Holliness Riaz Ahmed Gohar Shahi:
His Hollines Riaz Ahmed Gohar Shahi belongs to a village of Pakistan "Dhok Gohar Shah", which is located in City of Gujar khan, district Rawalpindi , province Punjab. His Hollines Real name is Riaz Ahmed and the suffix Gohar Shahi is from your family backgrounds.He is a fifth generation descendant of the Sufi Baba Gohar Ali Shah.
##  Mysterious Birth of Riaz Ahmed Gohar Shahi
His Holiness Riaz Ahmed Gohar Shahi graced this earth on 25 November 1941. His Hollines Mother shared an extraordinary story with one of his followers about his miraculous birth. She recounted that Gohar Shahi was not born in the usual way that other children are. When asked for details, she explained that even before his birth, the Holy Prophet Muhammad (peace be upon him) appeared to her in a dream and said, "We are going to give you Riaz." On the day of delivery, she recalled, she was resting and suddenly felt the sensation of a child pushing his legs within her. She woke up and was astonished to see a child already present near her in the room. The entire experience was beyond ordinary—she did not feel any pain, as though it was the divine birth of someone extraordinary who had arrived directly from the heavens. The room was filled with an enchanting fragrance and a profound sense of peace. She described Riaz as someone unlike any other child.
The followers of Riaz Ahmed Gohar Shahi firmly believe that his arrival on Earth was miraculous and did not involve a typical childbirth process. They regard Riaz as a divine personality Who came to this universe to guide humanity and reconnect them with God.
